pageProduct.name: Thompson's Ultra B 60 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's Ultra B provides a high potency balance of B vitamins and Magnesium and supports healthy stress response, nervous system and energy production
- Supports healthy nervous system
- Support during times of stress
- Supports energy production

Suitable For: Vegetarian/Vegan.

Boxed Contents: 60 Tablets

Size: 60 Tablets

Alcohol Free?: Yes

KEY FEATURES

• Helps support the healthy functioning of the nervous system
• Support during times of stress
• Supports energy production

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. Contains soyabean.

CAUTION

Keep out of reach of children. Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each tablet contans:
Thiamine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B1) 50mg
Riboflavin (Vitamin B2) 15mg
Nicotinamide (Vitamin B3) 50mg
Calcium Pantothenate 100mg
equiv. Pantothenic Acid (Vitamin B5)
91.6mg
Pyridoxine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B6) 25mg
equiv. Pyridoxine (Vitamin B6) 20.6mg
Folic Acid 100mcg
Cyanocobalamin (Vitamin B12)
25mcg
Biotin 25mcg
Choline Bitartrate 25mg
Inositol 25mg
Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C) 125mg
Calcium Ascorbate Dihydrate 125mg
equiv. Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C) 103mg
Total Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C) 228mg
d-alpha-Tocopherol Acid Succinate 25mg
equiv. Natural Vitamin E 30IU
Iron (as Amino Acid Chelate) 1mg
Magnesium (as Phosphate) 20.7mg
Manganese (as Sulfate Monohydrate) 1.6mg
Potassium (as Phosphate - Monobasic) 10mg
Zinc (as Amino Acid Chelate) 1.5mg
Lecithin 5mg
Herbal extract equiv. to dry:
Passiflora incarnata (Passionflower) herb top flowering 50mg
Valeriana officinalis (Valerian) root 50mg
Scutellaria lateriflora (Skullcap) herb 50mg
Powders:
Rosa canina (Rosehip) fruit 20mg
Petroselinum crispum (Parsley) herb 5mg
Nasturtium officinale (Watercress) 5mg

Allergen Contains: Soybean

Allergen Free From: Dairy| Egg| Fish| Gluten| Lactose| Nuts| Sesame Seeds

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Remove cap and recycle glass.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
